Backup:
<pre name="code">
ssh user@hostname "dd if=/dev/sda" | gzip -1 - | dd of=/backup.gz
</pre>

Recover:
<pre name="code">
dd if=backup.gz | gunzip -1 - | "dd of=/dev/sda" 
</pre>

